            "text": "Yes, do it carefully.",
            "translation": "بله, با دقت انجامش بده."
        },
        {
            "order": 7,
            "person": 2,
            "text": "What is at the bottom?",
            "translation": "پایین چه چیزی است؟"
        },
        {
            "order": 8,
