        },
        {
            "order": 9,
            "person": 2,
            "text": "Should I mark a point here?",
            "translation": "اینجا یک نقطه بگذارم؟"
        },
        {
            "order": 10,
            "person": 1,
            "text": "Yes, put a small dot on each edge.",
            "translation": "بله، روی هر لبه یک نقطه کوچک بگذار."
        },
        {
            "order": 11,
            "person": 2,
            "text": "What about an oval on top?",
            "translation": "یک بیضی هم بالا چطور؟"
        },
        {
            "order": 12,
            "person": 1,
            "text": "Good idea. If you make a mistake, just erase it.",
